deps.context: project(llvm   version 12.0.0   languages c cxx asm)

libs.content: find_library(iconv_library_path names iconv libiconv libiconv-2 c)
find_program(gold_executable names ${llvm_default_target_triple}-ld.gold ld.gold ${llvm_default_target_triple}-ld ld doc "the gold linker")
find_program(ld64_executable names ld doc "the ld64 linker")

find_program(sphinx_executable
             names sphinx-build sphinx-build2
             doc "path to sphinx-build executable")

find_program(llvmar_executable
  names llvm-ar
  doc "the llvm-ar executable"
  )

find_program(llvmnm_executable
  names llvm-nm
  doc "the llvm-nm executable"
  )

find_program(llvmranlib_executable
  names llvm-ranlib
  doc "the llvm-ranlib executable"
  )

find_program(llvm_doxygen_qhelpgenerator_path qhelpgenerator
      doc "path to the qhelpgenerator binary")
find_library(panel_libraries names panel doc "the curses panel library" quiet)

find_program(llvm_lit
                   names llvm-lit lit.py lit
                   paths "${llvm_main_src_dir}/utils/lit"
                   doc "path to lit.py")

find_program(llvm_lit
                   names llvm-lit lit.py lit
                   paths "${llvm_main_src_dir}/utils/lit"
                   doc "path to lit.py")

find_library(vtune_libraries libittnotify
    hints "${vtune_include_dirs}/.."
    paths ${dirs}
    path_suffixes lib32)

find_program(openmp_llvm_lit_executable
    names llvm-lit lit.py lit
    paths ${openmp_llvm_tools_dir})

find_library (
  libomptarget_dep_libelf_libraries
  names
    elf
  paths
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
    /opt/local/lib
    /sw/lib
    env library_path
    env ld_library_path)

find_library (
      libomptarget_dep_libffi_libraries
    names
      ffi
    hints
      ${libomptarget_search_libffi_libdir}
      ${libomptarget_search_libffi_library_dirs}
    paths
      /usr/lib
      /usr/local/lib
      /opt/local/lib
      /sw/lib
      env library_path
      env ld_library_path)

find_library (
  libomptarget_dep_veo_libraries
  names
    veo
  paths
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
    /opt/local/lib
    /sw/lib
    /opt/nec/ve/veos/lib64
    env library_path
    env ld_library_path)

find_library(
  libomptarget_dep_veosinfo_libraries
  names
    veosinfo
  paths
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
    /opt/local/lib
    /sw/lib
    /opt/nec/ve/veos/lib64
    env library_path
    env ld_library_path)
